I then waited fifteen minutes for my food because the staff seemed to be distracted about someone at drive through who decided to come in because he and the manager had an interest in each other and I was forgotten (the guy behind me got his food first and had arrived five minutes after me).  All the tables are dirty, and there's some weird pink splatter on the wall near where I'm sitting. Maybe it's from this morning and impossible to come off and there's a work order in place. Even right now after I've finished my food, I can  hear two men complaining that they need to find somewhere to sit that's clean and have no options, so the same young woman came over and cleaned their table.  Unless you're desperate, go to Subway or taco Bell up the street.
